title: Tis the Season for Weird Medical Questions
description: We're warming the December chill with another Sawbones Q+A, answering all the weird medical questions that can only be answered publicly, on a podcast. Questions about milk and lost limbs, mole hair, spontaneous UTIs, dead germs, where does the vaccine go, and sexy sneezing.
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin & Dr. Sydnee McElroy)
